### Record a deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: txn-dep-001

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "ZAR",
  "description": "Initial deposit"
}

### Record a withdrawal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: txn-wd-001

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "amount": 200.00,
  "currency": "ZAR",
  "description": "Cash withdrawal"
}

### Initiate a transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: xfer-001

{
  "sourceAccountId": 1,
  "targetAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "ZAR",
  "description": "Rent payment"
}

### Get transfer status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/{{transferId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get transactions for account
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/account/1?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get ledger entries for account
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/account/1/ledger?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
